{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_51_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 瑠依の疑問",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、瑠依ちゃん見んかった？\n先にレッスン室行ったんかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have you seen Rui-chan‚ Sumire-chan?\nI wonder if she went to the lesson room first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1468748927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。今、会議室で雑誌の打ち合わせをしてるみたい\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. It seems she's doing a magazine interview in a meeting room\nFor 'Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.206553189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやった、今日か！　アイドルのお願い聞いてくれる\nやつや。瑠依ちゃん、誕生日に何したいんやろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ it’s today! The one where they grant idols’ wishes.\nWhat do you think Rui wants to do for her birthday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "何かな～。私だったら、やりたいこと\n沢山あって決められないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder. If it were me‚\nI'd have too many things to decide~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4410824496,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3053.987372000002,
          "startTime": 30.4950698216
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "待った？　打ち合わせが長引いちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you wait long? The meeting ran a little long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4291852634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "気にせんでええよ、まだレッスンまで時間あるし\nそれより、企画何にしたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. We still have time before the lesson.\nSo‚ what did you wish for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333361944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "それなんだけど……決まらなくて困ってるの\nやりたいことが全然思いつかないのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the thing… I'm having trouble deciding.\nI can’t think of anything I want to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7827921709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあさ、一緒に考えない！？\n三人集まればなんとかの知恵って言うし。ね、優ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ why don’t we think about it together?!\nTwo heads are better than one‚ as they say! Right‚ Yu-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8494588376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ええやん、ええやん、楽しいやーん\nすみれちゃんええこと言うなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ sounds fun~!\nSumire-chan‚ that’s a great idea!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9000028611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっともう、二人とも楽しんでるだけじゃない\nでも……思いつかないのは事実だしお願いしようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you two are just having fun.\nBut… it’s true that I can't think of anything… Maybe I should ask for help?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9462470156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "まず、そもそもの疑問なんだけれど\n普通の高校生って誕生日に何しているの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ I have a fundamental question.\nWhat do normal high school students do on their birthdays…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9966018041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、瑠依ちゃんらしい疑問やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that’s such a Rui-like question.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3299351375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちが思うに……やっぱ彼氏と過ごすんちゃう？\n特別な日やもん、二人っきりで熱い誕生日を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think… They probably spend it with their boyfriend.\nIt's a special day‚ so they have a passionate birthday together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9666695278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ！　優、ふざけないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ stop messing around!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0444479783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、冗談やんか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ I was just kidding~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1777813117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "彼氏もだけど大切な人と一緒に過ごすんじゃないかな？\n家族とか、友達と遊んだりとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They might spend time with important people.\nLike their family or by going out with friends!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3527750809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、クラスの子らは誕生日にカラオケ\n行っとったなぁ～。めっちゃ盛り上がったみたいやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That reminds me‚ the kids in my class went to karaoke\non their birthdays. It seems like they had a lot of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333412807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……友達と過ごす誕生日ね\n経験ないかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Spending your birthday with friends.\nI don’t think I've experienced that before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3225028037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃない！？\nそれを叶えてもらおうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it!\nLet’s ask for that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9225028037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "友達と、普通の高校生の誕生日を過ごす企画\n確かに、凄く楽しそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spending my birthday like a normal high schooler with friends…\nThat actually sounds really fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9891694704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ということは……\n友達がおらな話にならんな～？　ちらっちらっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That means…\nWe need friends for that to work… Glance‚ glance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7000079473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ここにぴったりな二人がいると思う！　ちらっちらっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we have the perfect two people right here! Glance‚ glance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8123893577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ぷ、ふふ……もう、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-fufu… What are you two talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4123893577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うちらなら瑠依ちゃんに誰よりも最高の\n誕生日をプレゼント出来るやんか。な、すみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can give Rui-chan the best birthday ever‚\nRight‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0609608353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、瑠依ちゃんのお誕生日企画\nぜひ、お手伝いさせてほしいな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes. We’d love to\nhelp you with your birthday project!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4156094549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう。きっと素敵な企画になるわね\nこちらこそ、お手伝いをお願いしてもいいかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you. I'm sure it will be a wonderful project.\nI’d love for you to help me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9489427882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0489305812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.0489305812
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.0489305812
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.4155972479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんのお誕生日、どこに行けばいいかなー\n東京の有名な場所はどう？　浅草とか動物園とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where should we take Rui-chan for her birthday?\nHow about a famous place in Tokyo? Like Asakusa or the zoo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4155972479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.4156053859
    },
    {
